rows.label: qst201219_0030
rows.name:
The smile!
Good to know it's in working order.

rows.label: qst201219_0050
rows.name:
It's like you got really into it there, and
a smile just crept over your face, all natural-like.

rows.label: qst201219_0060
rows.name: Hey, Seori. Why don't you go check on Mikumari?

rows.label: qst201219_0080
rows.name:
Come on. You've both been putting your noses to the
grindstone. Go celebrate together!

rows.label: qst201219_0090
rows.name:
I didn't really do anything.
It was all thanks to Mikumari.

rows.label: qst201219_0100
rows.name:
She just doesn't give up,
and it's got all the townfolk smiling.

rows.label: qst201219_0110
rows.name: Nah. It's thanks to both of you.

rows.label: qst201219_0130
rows.name:
I think Mikumari doesn't give up because of
you, Seori.

rows.label: qst201219_0140
rows.name:
It's thanks to that synergy that exists between you that the
townsfolk are smiling.

rows.label: qst201219_0150
rows.name:
Siblings have a duty to look out for each other, and amplify each
other. This is what's happening here.

rows.label: qst201219_0230
rows.name:
My sister gets a bit lonely if I
leave her alone for too long.

rows.label: qst201219_0240
rows.name:
Hey, what are you saying...
I can manage by myself!

rows.label: qst201219_0250
rows.name:
Hang on!
Did you just...call me sister...?

rows.label: qst201219_0290
rows.name:
Hey! Come on!
You know we're about to start!

rows.label: qst201219_0320
rows.name: I don't know what you mean...
